reviewText: Arrived on time, undamaged, exactly as described. Thomas the Train is timeless & the kids love it.
Very entertaining like all the Thomas and Friends videos.  I would give all the Thomas and Friends videos ten stars if it was possible.  The high quality is amazing.
My little guy lobes a Big Day for Thomas. Thank you
The best for my grandson, he loves Thomas the train
Good for a grandson for Christmas....Anything Thomas is good!
My 2 year old loves Thomas and this was the perfect addition to his collection.
Niece and nephews loved it. A couple bucks for hours of entertainment for the kids on a rainy day, thats a deal.
Good movie to entertain my 2 year old boy.
